                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/7978: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-12-30T12:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 30, 1926—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>312. Your No. 642 of December 28, 10 a.m. As other powers have made no inquiries
                    of the Department respecting this matter, will it not be sufficient for you to
                    inform your interested colleagues?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
